data.description: This sprawling ranch offers peace & tranquility, away from the hustle & bustle of everyday life, while also offering the convenience of being minutes away from all the amenities of Tularosa, Alamogordo & the back gate to HAFB. Whether your dream is to have horses or other animals, plant a nice big garden or raise a family, this is the right place for you! With lush sprawling pastures, a nice  big barn with spacious stalls, riding arenas & round pen, it provides an ideal environment for any animal enthusiast. 25 yrs. ago an alaskan bush pilot/guide had enough of the cold weather in the north country & found this oasis in the desert. Naming it the Good Moose Ranch after an alaskan native legend. He raised & trained horses, grew alfalfa & many big gardens over the years. This property includes a spacious 5 bed, 2 bath farmhouse with an eat in kitchen, large living room with vaulted ceilings, and extra hobby room, perfect for any family.
